        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span>Despite covering the entire face, this alabaster mask does not hinder vision or other senses. Wearing the mask grants a +1 item bonus to Performance checks while acting, orating, performing comedy, or singing.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span>The mask grants a +2 bonus and can be activated.<br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">R</span>&nbsp;envision (fortune);&nbsp;<strong>Frequency</strong>&nbsp;once per day;&nbsp;<strong>Trigger</strong>&nbsp;You fail a Performance check that benefits from the mask&rsquo;s bonus;&nbsp;<strong>Effect</strong>&nbsp;You change the mask&rsquo;s character and reroll the Performance check, using the second result.</p>\n<p><span><br /><br /></span></p>",
